{"article_id":"PUPUBWem5SOkZHkD","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Iraqi Gen. Qassam Soleimani was taken out","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"because the government had intelligence","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"``","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"which we believe","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"was very strong ''","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"that showed","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"the commander and those","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"with whom he was plotting","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"were `` looking to kill American diplomats and soldiers in significant numbers '' in upcoming days ,","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"National Security Adviser Robert O'Brien said Tuesday .","depth":4},{"id":10,"text":"`` I can tell you","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"that there were plans","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"that were being made","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"and Soleimani was in the midst of that plotting , ''","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"O'Brien told Fox News ' `` Fox and Friends . ''","depth":5},{"id":15,"text":"`` That 's why he was traveling in the region in Damascus and Beirut and Baghdad ,","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"to conspire with people","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"to attack American facilities","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"that contained diplomat soldiers , airmen , Marines , Coast Guardsmen .","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"We were ,","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"the president was very concerned about that activity .","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"Soleimani and the Iranian regime knew exactly what they were doing .","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"What they did was underestimated the president and his restraint .","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"'' In recent months , Iran has downed several drones ,","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"attacked Saudi Arabia 's ARAMCO ,","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"and taken several other actions ,","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"and President Donald Trump has been `` very restrained , ''","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"said O'Brien .","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"`` The president tried to open negotiations with the Iranians , ''","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"`` Remember ,","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"he offered to speak with them unconditionally .","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"They took that as a sign of weakness ...","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"they made a bad mistake","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"in how they read his restraint ,","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"which was admirable . ''","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"Meanwhile , Soleimani also had been heavily involved from the early days in Iran 's nuclear program ,","depth":5},{"id":37,"text":"said O'Brien ,","depth":5},{"id":38,"text":"and was not to be traveling outside Iran","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"because of United Nations sanctions .","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"His death will have an `` effect '' on the nuclear program , as will the Trump administration 's policy of peace through strength ,","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"he added .","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"`` The president made it very clear","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"that Iran will not have a nuclear weapon","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"and I think","depth":6},{"id":45,"text":"we have got a lot of friends and allies in the region and Europe committed to that outcome , ''","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"said O'Brien .","depth":4},{"id":47,"text":"O'Brien also discussed the decision","depth":4},{"id":48,"text":"to deny Iranian Foreign Affairs Minister Mohammad Zarif 's entry visa","depth":5},{"id":49,"text":"to allow him to enter the United States","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"to attend a meeting of the UN Security Council ,","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"saying","depth":5},{"id":52,"text":"Secretary of State Pompeo did not believe it to be the `` right time ''","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"for Zarif to come into the country .","depth":6},{"id":54,"text":"`` Whenever he comes to New York ,","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"he spreads propaganda , ''","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"said O'Brien .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"p